Description
-----------

Enables/disables the display of material names under the crosshair.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_showSurfaceInfo [bool]

Parameters
----------

-   [bool] - Enables/disables the display of material names under the
    crosshair.
    -   0 - Disabled
    -   1 - Enabled

